class=&#34;mdx-badge mdx-badge--china&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;mdx-badge__icon&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;../../help/docs/contributing.md#符号&#34; title=&#34;中国版独有&#34;&gt;:material-inbox-full:&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;...&lt;/h1&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/server/apollo/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 05:30:09 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_updated.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/server/apollo/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/docs/server/apollo.png" type="image/png" length="15286" /> </item> <item> <title>过时教程</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;过时教程&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;过时教程收纳仍有兼容性价值、但不应混入最新版主线的内容。这里的“过时”不等于“无用”：很多旧格式仍会被游戏接受，旧项目也需要维护；只是新项目不应该再把它们当作默认方案。&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;/// warning | 新项目优先阅读最新版教程 如果你正在创建新附加包，请先阅读最新版主线教程。只有在维护旧包、迁移旧包...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/outdated/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 05:30:09 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_updated.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/outdated/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/guides/outdated/index.png" type="image/png" length="10480" /> </item> <item> <title>旧版中国版Apollo网络服流程</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;旧版中国版Apollo网络服流程&lt;span class=&#34;mdx-badge mdx-badge--china&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;mdx-badge__icon&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;../../help/docs/contributing.md#符号&#34; title=&#34;中国版独有&#34;&gt;:material-inbox-full:&lt;/a&gt;&amp;lt;...&lt;/h1&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/outdated/china-legacy-apollo/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 05:30:09 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_updated.xml">基岩文